Deemos aimed and fired his cannon at Reptilica, Inzola firing at
Bloodystrike. Deemos smiled at BrightBlade. Inzola coughed a few times and
laughed.

"yes, we are Preds, the Alliance are not the most powerful after all!"
Deemos said to BrightBlade...
----- Original Message -----
From: "Moon Mist" <shadowwarrior_ax@...>
To: <nbwrpg@egroups.com>
Sent: Tuesday, July 11, 2000 2:27 AM
Subject: Re: Neo Beast Wars




* BrightBlade tensed as she saw Deemos come up to her, then seeing Inzola
come up as well. But when they greeted her and bowed she then straightened
herself up a bit and then straightened her fur.which had been ruffled due to
the sudden shock of them being there. She had almost thought that they were
Alliance bots, glad as heck that they worn't.
But then she realized that she was just outside the Alliance base, being in
the wrong place at the wrong time if they detected her!
She was just about to excuse herself and leave when Reptilica and
Bloodystrike suddenly appeared, BrightBlade nearly jumping in surprise and
transforming.ready to battle.
With a growl she glared at Bloodystrike as he aimed his gun at them all,
transforming and simply standing there. She leaned her back against a tree
and simply stayed there, bowing her head, crossing her arms and closing her
optics. Simply there and acting as if she wasn't phased by their presence at
all.
She then heard Deemos speak, then finding out the couple were married. She
smirked. But she then looked over at the couple.*

" Those two aren't Predacons, they're the ENEMIES of the Predacons. Alliance
slags.*

" She pointed to Reptilica,*

" That one's Scale Face,"

*Then pointed at Bloodystrike,*

" And that one's BloodyNose."

* She then sighed and looked ahead of herself, a smile on her face.*

" I'M the Predacon."
